and is in serious condition.

107
00:09:35.225 --> 00:09:37.516
In a quick
and violent operation.

108
00:09:37.517 --> 00:09:41.808
eight men and one woman
used a Willys Aero

109
00:09:41.809 --> 00:09:45.517
