121
00:10:19.434 --> 00:10:20.642
What happened?

122
00:10:21.183 --> 00:10:23.933
I'm still shaking.
It was fucked up.

123
00:10:23.934 --> 00:10:25.058
What happened?

124
00:10:25.059 --> 00:10:26.558
Watch your language. Veroca!

125
00:10:26.559 --> 00:10:27.766
